full_text: Atlanta looks a lot like the 2021 first half team and not the 2021 second half team... down 11-0 in San Diego

This one’s insane: since OAA (Outs Above Average) became a stat in 2017, Francisco Lindor has ranked in the 100th percentile 3 times, 99th once, and 98th once. That’s just insanely consistent elite defense.
Eduardo Escobar’s career high walk rate before 2022 was 8.2% in 2018. He’s at 29.6% so far this year.
